Start Google App Engine environment in your computer and create a simple one-page web application.

Algorithm:

1.Start.

2.Download Google App Engine SDK from Python official page.

3.Install the SDK which also installs App Engine and related tools.

4.Install Python 2.7 and configure its path.

5.Open App Engine Launcher from Start Menu.

6.Create a new project:

  -Click File and create new application.
  -Select your project folder.
  -Make sure your folder has app.yaml, app.py.

7.Set Python path to Python 2.7 path.

8.Click Start on the launcher.

9.Open web browser and go to http://localhost:8080.

10.This will show the web app that we have created.

11.Stop the server.
